      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，主键id和customer_id外键都记下了，类型都是bigint。那这个订单实体还需要记录哪些业务字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "id",
        "customer_id"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "物流相关的要有shipping_address收货地址和delivery_method配送方式，这两个都用text类型。还有一个很重要的时间戳ordered_at，要精确到带时区的，用timestamp with time zone。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "shipping_address",
        "delivery_method",
        "ordered_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：shipping_address（text）、delivery_method（text）、ordered_at（timestamp_with_time_zone）。接下来是金额字段吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
